                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-88-off472 t17900424-88-cd473"></join>, a flock and feather bed, value 12 s. a bolster, value 2 s. two blankets, value 4 s. a stuff coverlid, value 2 s. 6 d. a saucepan, value 1 s. a pan, value 9 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900424-88-victim782" type="victimName">
